snippet.title: Space Dash
snippet.description:
Space Dash is a space-themed endless runner, where collecting oxygen is needed to stay alive.

Play Here: https://jackv24.itch.io/space-dash

This game was created over a six week period, with the following team:

Designers
 - Shannon Cross
 - Casey Lehmann
 - Lucy Andreasen
Artists
 - Bailey O'Brien
 - Richard Jones
 - Josh McKay
Programmers
 - Jack Vine
